  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build A School for 200 street children in Ghana</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aim at addressing illiteracy among underserved children by constructing three classrooms to provide them with a serene learning environment. Currently, we managed to mobilise the children under an open nature shelter where we meet everyday to study. Situation on ground such as rainfall and frequent bumping of people into the premises does not permit sound studies. With portable classrooms we guarantee these children right to quality education no matter their socio-economic background</narrative>
  </description>
